I would be really surprised if
we ever see another bull

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:06.520
market of the length that
we had during--

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:07.280
what, '82 to--

00:11:07.280 --> 00:11:09.300
JOHN DEL VECCHIO:
1982 to 2001.

