00:21:02.270 --> 00:21:03.510
for revenue and earnings.

00:21:03.510 --> 00:21:05.880
So management's going to do
whatever it takes, by and

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:09.520
large, to keep the stock price
up, keep the stock options up,

00:21:09.520 --> 00:21:12.220
protect their own job,
make everybody happy.

00:21:12.220 --> 00:21:15.680
It's all driven by
expectations.

00:21:15.680 --> 00:21:17.570
If you think about an income
statement, you have revenue on

00:21:17.570 --> 00:21:19.470
the top and net income
on the bottom.

00:21:19.470 --> 00:21:21.660
So the earnings that a company
reports are the least

00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:23.980
important line item that
