combined entities all the way

00:29:44.410 --> 00:29:46.210
back into history.

00:29:46.210 --> 00:29:49.570
So even if I'm flush with cash,
I can still obscure the

00:29:49.570 --> 00:29:52.020
revenue growth, I can obscure
my cash flow.

00:29:52.020 --> 00:29:53.980
I can do all kinds of
shenanigans on the balance

00:29:53.980 --> 00:29:57.390
sheet to move expenses off
there, to create all kinds of

00:29:57.390 --> 00:29:59.130
goodwill that doesn't
really exist.

00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:01.270
And all that's just leading to
is big write-downs in the

00:30:01.270 --> 00:30:03.310
future, and ultimately
